Package: Rfmalloc
Title: Memory-Mapped File Allocation for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure", email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides memory-mapped file allocation capabilities for R using 
    the fmalloc library. Supports both custom allocators and ALTREP-based 
    memory-mapped vectors for efficient persistent storage and memory usage. fmalloc from https://github.com/yasukata/fmalloc
    and custom allocators from https://gist.github.com/s-u/6712c97ca74181f5a1a5
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    tinytest
SystemRequirements: C++11, pthreads
URL: https://github.com/sounkou-bio/fmalloc
BugReports: https://github.com/sounkou-bio/fmalloc/issues
